title: Hackathon prize adjustment
body:
This is a follow up on this proposal, originally sent to the builders working group: https://snapshot.org/#/r-wave.eth/proposal/0x219c31f61a54cfcf06110a5b62320d4ea3c5ca71d1e240bfdbb71b314fbfa677

The initial proposal was for 1K and 1K, whereas the prizes should have been 1K and 2K.

Transactions are below:
https://etherscan.io/tx/0x919bec282a81d3f3b03ab61da28bad9535ec0646b2385435a99c7aec45c0e61e
https://etherscan.io/tx/0x25323c628b541b8e5869cd81ca9825e611da4b5eae03ea36e5c7e7d78e02e3fa

total refund: 2051.17 + 1056.16 = 3107.33
funds to be sent to: 0xa15Ca74e65bf72730811ABF95163E89aD9b9DFF6 on polygon. Consider the other proposal void.
author: 0xa15Ca74e65bf72730811ABF95163E89aD9b9DFF6
